---
title: Nan's Creamy Chicken Penne with Parmesan & Hidden Carrot
description: This saucy creation uses a creamy tomato sauce to coat penne, with chunks of tender chicken and flavoursome Parmesan.
Add grated carrot that melts into the sauce and baby spinach that gently wilts when tossed with the pasta, and you’ve got a new recipe that's sure to please everyone.

